## Notes:
- For production deployment on Netlify, add these as environment variables in the Netlify dashboard
- The NEXTAUTH_SECRET should be a random 32-character string
- Make sure NEXTAUTH_URL matches your deployed URL
- For local development, use http://localhost:3000 as NEXTAUTH_URL
- Create a GitHub OAuth App at https://github.com/settings/applications/new
- Set the Authorization callback URL to: https://yah-admin.netlify.app/api/auth/callback/github